 Reason for being 


Membership of the Senior Director, Certification and Accounting, the Technician's mission is to maintain the accounting records of the clients, to accompany them in their accounting accountants, the various paid interfaces and the various operations. Accountants.


 Key activities 



 Perform customer accounting assigned to it (book holding, balance of bank accounts and large accounts books); 

 Prepare and count the end of the month and end-of-year entries; 

 Make the regularization scriptures including the calculation of depreciation of fixed assets; 

 perform payroll processing and calculating the deductions at the source; 

 prepare government discounts, fiscal sheets and summaries such as T4, T5, Relevant 1 and Relevé 3; 

 Prepare the Company's overall results (SSD) on a monthly basis, trimes trielle or semi-annual; 

 configure, during new clients, their accounting in Sage 50; 

 Train clients on the accounting software and / or other aspects of their accounting; 

