Job description


The role will encompass 2 main tasks – providing invoice processing and AR support for our NL location, processing payroll and completing all payroll activities for 3 provinces NS, PEI and NL (85 employees currently, hourly and salary).





*Other activities included but not limited to*



Code and enter Project invoices into the accounting software (Quickbooks) as directed;

Assist with other Project accounts payable tasks as needed, such as printing cheques, assisting with setting up vendor files for digital banking, filing vendor documents;

Maintain the payroll system for satellite offices, including set up of new employees, responding to employee inquiries, revising timesheets, preparing monthly remittances for Manager review;

Scanning documents, organizing digital folders;

Downloading and organizing monthly bank statements and cheques;

Assisting with banking activities such as making and recording deposits, making payments at the bank;

Organizing support documents for year end working papers files;

Entering credit card transactions into Quickbooks;

Assisting Controller in all accounting tasks as needed.



*What we seek*



1-2 years experience within an accountant or payable position

Quickbooks or Simply Accounting is an asset

Well-spoken, organized, willingness to learn

Positive and friendly team player, with a great attitude





Please apply if you have the experience listed above, only qualifying candidates will be contacted.

